'</p>',
'',
'<p>',
'   <b>Move Loaded File</b><br> ',
'    Provides the end user the ability of moving a file from STAGE to LOADED,this is very useful if the process crashes just after the file has been loaded leaving the file stuck in STAGE.',
'</p>',
'',
'',
'<h3> Application Dependencies </h3> ',
