,p_plug_source=>wwv_flow_utilities.join(wwv_flow_t_varchar2(
'<h4>Oracle Load Process</h4>',
'<ul>',
'  <li>Resides in the <b>RDM_LOAD</b> schema on the Oracle Server</li>',
'  <li>Consists of the following Oracle procedures:</li>',
'   <ul> ',
'    <li>BOA_LOAD_QUEUE_WATCH</li>',
'    <li>BOA_FILE_WATCH_PROGR</li>',
'    <li>BOA_UNIX_FILES_PROGR</li>',
'    <li>PROCESS_NEW_FEEDS</li>',
'    <li>PROCESS_LOAD_QUEUE</li>',
'    <li>UPDATE_LOAD_STATUS</li>',
'    <li>BOA_CREATE_UNIX_JOB</li>',
'    <li>BOA_CHECK_UNIX_JOBS</li>',
'    </ul> ',
' </ul>',
'<p> When notified by <b>DBMS_SCHEDULER FILE_WATCHER</b> that a new file has arrived copies it from SOURCE to STAGE by creating an external job, <b>BOA_CREATE_UNIX_JOB</b> and inserts the file name into the BOA File Watch Queue<br><br> ',
'<b>BOA_FILE_WATCH_PROGR:</b> checks the BOA File Watch Queue (hourly) for files that haven''t been processed yet, checks their status with <b>BOA_CHECK_UNIX_JOBS</b>. If the file was moved into STAGE successfully adds the file name to the BOA Load Que'
||'ue and BOA File Load Queue.<br><br>',
'<b>PROCESS_NEW_FEEDS</b> Scheduled to run daily at 5:00 PM checks BOA Load Queue for files that haven''t been loaded yet if any found calls <b> PROCESS_LOAD_QUEUE</b> to load the files.',
'<br><br> ',
'<b>PROCESS_LOAD_QUEUE:</b>',
'<ul>',
'   <li>Checks each new entry in BOA Load Queue to see if it has been loaded before</li>',
'   <li> Logs the file name to BOfA Files Processed</li>',
'   <li> Assigns the File name to the external table</li> ',
'   <li> Loads the file into a staging table using the external table</li> ',
'   <li> Checks for any loading issues</li>',
'   <li> Calls <b> UPDATE_LOAD_STATUS</b> to update the server logs</li>',
'   <li> Calls <b>BOA_LOAD_QUEUE_WATCH</b> to move the file out of STAGE into LOADED</li>',
'</ul>',
'<br>',
'<b> BOA_LOAD_QUEUE_WATCH:</b><br>Creates external job to move the file from STAGE to LOADED using BOA_CREATE_UNIX_JOB and adds file name and job number to BOA File Load Queue<br><br>',
'<b>BOA_UNIX_FILES_PROGR:</b><br>Scheduled hourly to check jobs listed as incomplete in BOA File Load Queue for success or failure and creates an external job for the next step in the flow.  ',
'</p>'))
,p_plug_query_row_template=>1
